headline: UPS Leans Into $9 Billion Automation Strategy with Robotics Rollout
summary: UPS is reportedly investing $120 million in 400 autonomous truck-unloading robots from Pickle Robot, accelerating its warehouse automation push.

headline: UPS Bets $120 Million on Robot Army to Slash Costs and Crush Delivery Bottlenecks
summary: Pickle Robot's AI-powered unloaders are coming for the shipping docks--backed by UPS's $9 billion automation overhaul.
